    <acqinfo id="aspace_946b4647baeef521e78964814a355bdb">
      <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
      <p>Gifts of Mary Ann Riviere (1998) and Rosemary Cassel (2015). Source of acquisition of the Metz-Greene family genealogical file is unknown.</p>
    </acqinfo>
    <scopecontent id="aspace_f31511d6baae6ecd247096b8c19ebfb0">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>The collection consists of genealogical records relating to Brooklyn families that have been collected by Brooklyn Historical Society, dating from 1892 to 1998. Families include Allen, Bueker, Foster, Greene, Metz, Sparacino, Walker, and others. Types of materials include death certificates, marriage certificates, photographs, and clippings.</p>
    </scopecontent>
